article_title: Time is right for Michigan nurse practitioners
article_text:
Midland, MI (48640)

Today

Mixed clouds and sun with scattered thunderstorms. High 84F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 60%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening. Partly cloudy skies after midnight. Low 63F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 60%.

article_metadata.author: Ann Sheehan

og.description: Maryland recently became the 21st state (plus Washington, D.C.) to allow full practice authority for nurse practitioners. I am looking forward to adding Michigan to this list. Nurse practitioners’ aim
